  "elements": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_title",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 10,
      "text": "AI Modules — Voice, Narrative, World, Public Opinion",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "AI Modules — Voice, Narrative, World, Public Opinion",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_common",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 55,
      "text": "Common pattern (all 4 modules):",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "Common pattern (all 4 modules):",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_common_list",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 85,
      "text": "• Each has its own page route (e.g. /character/[id]/voice)\n• Each has its own Client component + API route\n• All use SSE streaming with chatCompletionStream\n• All use useAiSettings() for provider/model/apiKey\n• All have custom system prompts (editable in AppSetting)\n• All have AbortController + 90s timeout\n• All have their own PromptsPanel for prompt editing\n• All save to database via Server Actions (updateCharacterVoice, etc.)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "• Each has its own page route (e.g. /character/[id]/voice)\n• Each has its own Client component + API route\n• All use SSE streaming with chatCompletionStream\n• All use useAiSettings() for provider/model/apiKey\n• All have custom system prompts (editable in AppSetting)\n• All have AbortController + 90s timeout\n• All have their own PromptsPanel for prompt editing\n• All save to database via Server Actions (updateCharacterVoice, etc.)",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r_voice_bg",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 210,
      "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "boundElements": [{"id": "t_voice_bg", "type": "text"}]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_voice_bg",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 248,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "VOICE MODULE",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "r_voice_bg",
      "originalText": "VOICE MODULE",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_voice_items",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 280,
      "text": "• VoiceClient.tsx\n• API: /api/ai/voice (POST SSE)\n• Prompt: promt/promt_dialog.md\n  or VOICE_PROMPT from AppSetting\n• Generates: 8-10 dialogue scenes\n  showing character voice in\n  different situations\n• Output: raw markdown in textarea\n  auto-saved to character.voice\n• Typewriter effect with scroll lock",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "• VoiceClient.tsx\n• API: /api/ai/voice (POST SSE)\n• Prompt: promt/promt_dialog.md\n  or VOICE_PROMPT from AppSetting\n• Generates: 8-10 dialogue scenes\n  showing character voice in\n  different situations\n• Output: raw markdown in textarea\n  auto-saved to character.voice\n• Typewriter effect with scroll lock",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r_narrative_bg",
      "x": 410,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 210,
      "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "boundElements": [{"id": "t_narrative_bg", "type": "text"}]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_narrative_bg",
      "x": 415,
      "y": 248,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "NARRATIVE MODULE",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "r_narrative_bg",
      "originalText": "NARRATIVE MODULE",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_narrative_items",
      "x": 425,
      "y": 280,
      "text": "• NarrativeClient.tsx\n• API: /api/ai/narrative (POST SSE)\n• Prompt: NARRATIVE_PROMPT\n  from AppSetting or DEFAULT_\n• Generates: literary prose\n  description of character\n• Output: HTML/markdown with\n  typewriter effect\n• Saved to character.narrative\n  via updateCharacterNarrative",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "• NarrativeClient.tsx\n• API: /api/ai/narrative (POST SSE)\n• Prompt: NARRATIVE_PROMPT\n  from AppSetting or DEFAULT_\n• Generates: literary prose\n  description of character\n• Output: HTML/markdown with\n  typewriter effect\n• Saved to character.narrative\n  via updateCharacterNarrative",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
