    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_world_items",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 520,
      "text": "• WorldElementForm.tsx\n• API: /api/ai/world (POST SSE)\n• 2 modes: Generate (new) + Expand\n• Categories: location, faction,\n  history, rule, dictionary, other\n• Prompt: WORLD_SYSTEM_PROMPT,\n  WORLD_GENERATE_PROMPT,\n  WORLD_EXPAND_PROMPT\n• Output: free text in textarea\n  auto-saved via updateWorldElement",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "• WorldElementForm.tsx\n• API: /api/ai/world (POST SSE)\n• 2 modes: Generate (new) + Expand\n• Categories: location, faction,\n  history, rule, dictionary, other\n• Prompt: WORLD_SYSTEM_PROMPT,\n  WORLD_GENERATE_PROMPT,\n  WORLD_EXPAND_PROMPT\n• Output: free text in textarea\n  auto-saved via updateWorldElement",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
