    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_public_items",
      "x": 425,
      "y": 520,
      "text": "• PublicClient.tsx\n• API: /api/ai/public (POST SSE)\n• Prompt: PUBLIC_PROMPT\n  from AppSetting or DEFAULT_\n• 5 roles: friend, acquaintance,\n  colleague, partner, ex\n• Input: full character data\n  + narrative text\n• Output: opinions per role in\n  markdown → parsed to form fields\n• Saved to character via\n  updateCharacterPublicOpinions",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "• PublicClient.tsx\n• API: /api/ai/public (POST SSE)\n• Prompt: PUBLIC_PROMPT\n  from AppSetting or DEFAULT_\n• 5 roles: friend, acquaintance,\n  colleague, partner, ex\n• Input: full character data\n  + narrative text\n• Output: opinions per role in\n  markdown → parsed to form fields\n• Saved to character via\n  updateCharacterPublicOpinions",
      "autoResize": true
    },
